title: Famous' Destiny The Monster In The Forest
description: Famous may have freed the princess, but her journey is far from over. Daniel is still out there threatening the very safety of her and her family. The monster in the forest has drawn the attention of more and more people. Join Famous as Jeremiah sends her on a quest to meet her birth family and solve the mystery of the monster in the forest. Will she be able to solve this mystery and fulfill her destiny? Or will Daniel trap her forever?
author: Alexis Anicque
